item.title: I have 2 questions
item.dc:creator: @zubmage zubmage
item.description:
@zubmage wrote:

Answer to Second Question:

Search for in Client.Java (using CTRL + F) for “Safe Zone” or whatever your safe zones are called.
Another one should say “Wildy” or “Safezone” but be in the “wildy” section. Change that Safezone into Wildy.
